«Reuben Allerhand 
Went to St. Stephen's School and often played here. 
We will always remember the love and laughter he 
brought to the lives of his family and friends."№
¶Harold Swindells 
Co-founder of Bath Postal Museum
He enjoyed walking in this park 
and liked to stop and look at every tree. 
This Always made him smile 
because he loved trees"Щ
